Golf_Club\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The gold medal\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"the neck\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic champion\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"the four majors\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"Pinehurst\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 425}, {\"ngram\": \"the Open\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"the past month\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Albatross Course, with its long fairways, fast greens and tricky bunkers was the venue for Europe's remarkable victory in 2018 when they regained the Ryder Cup from the United States.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9358232852143047, \"rank\": 0.048537800474738185, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Albatross Course\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"its long fairways\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"fast greens\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"tricky bunkers\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe's remarkable victory\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ryder Cup\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Will it be the course always remembered in Ireland as the place where Shane Lowry powered his way to Olympic gold?\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9922104616240425, \"rank\": 0.003840443079388003, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Re